                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The energy uncertainty at the first foil in",
                "the stack was estimated to be 0.3 MeV increasing up to",
                "1.5 MeV at the last foil due to the energy straggling",
                "and the uncertainty on the target thickness."
